[{"source": "https://www.popsci.com/feed/", "title": "Grizzlies are getting killed by roads, but the risks are bigger than roadkill", "description": "<div class=\"Article-thumbnail orgnc-SingleImage orgnc-SingleImage--center orgnc-SingleImage--hasCaption\">\n                    <div class=\"orgnc-SingleImage-wrapper\"><img alt=\"Grizzly bear mom and cubs crossing road in Yellowstone National Park\" class=\"orgnc-SingleImage-image webfeedsFeaturedVisual wp-post-image\" height=\"811\" src=\"https://www.popsci.com/uploads/2023/09/25/grizzly-bear-road-yellowstone-national-park.jpg?auto=webp&amp;width=1440&amp;height=811.44\" style=\"display: block; margin: auto; margin-bottom: 5px;\" width=\"1440\" /></div><div class=\"orgnc-SingleImage-caption\">Roadside encounters with grizzly bears can be dangerous, but not in the way you'd think. <span class=\"orgnc-SingleImage-credit\"><a href=\"https://depositphotos.com/photo/grizzly-bear-wild-386512376.html\">Deposit Photos</a></span></div></div><p>From highways to scenic backcountry routes, America's vast network of roads poses a slew of dangers to bears, mountain lions, and moose.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://w", "link": "https://www.popsci.com/environment/mammals-mortalities-roads/", "date_published": "2023-09-25T22:00:00+00:00", "bookmarked": false, "dead": null, "artist": "Popular Science", "album": "Popular Science", "user": null, "language": "en-US", "thumbnail": null}, {"source": "https://www.popsci.com/feed/", "title": "The best 3D modeling software in 2023", "description": "<div class=\"Article-thumbnail orgnc-SingleImage orgnc-SingleImage--center orgnc-SingleImage--productTable\">\n                    <div class=\"orgnc-SingleImage-wrapper\"><img alt=\"The best 3D modeling software brings characters, animations, art, models, and more to life.\" class=\"orgnc-SingleImage-image webfeedsFeaturedVisual wp-post-image\" height=\"936\" src=\"https://www.popsci.com/uploads/2023/09/25/best-3d-modeling-software.jpg?auto=we